title: The Beauty of Flaws and Imperfections
description:
Sadie welcomes Caitlin Crosby to the podcast. Caitlin is an actress, singer, songwriter, entrepreneur and founder of The Giving Keys. They discuss the beauty of flaws and imperfections, and how those can lead to your unique calling and vision.
